// the line below is .stignore's content, i.e. put this in the root of your sync folder(s) (where .stfolder resides)
// main reason for include is because syncthing then syncs this file too, and updates don't ruin my careful ignore project ;-)
// see also https://forum.syncthing.net/t/useful-stignore-patterns/1175

!zsh_history

.direnv/
.terraform/
.cache/
.venv/
temp/
sessions/
node_modules/

(?d)__pycache__
(?d).DS_Store
(?d).ansible/
*.log
maintenance.lock
